description:
Use Fast n easy Live Flight Tracker and Airplane Radar & Track Plane's worldwide also get detailed airport information. You can Quickly check the status on the map, all current air planes from all over the world are displayed with air traffic control. Flight Radar is a range of tools at your disposal to track your trips and view progress on a tracking map.  Live Flight Status Tracker and  provide a comprehensive range of airport information and services all over the world. Keep track of your Plane details. Get updates as soon as your flight gets canceled, active, Diverted, incident or Delayed in Real time. Get in-depth information about; arrivals, departures, terminal & gates, bus type, Speed & altitude meter and much more. Live Flight Status Tracker is the most convenient app you will get on Google Play Store Travel safe & enjoy your tour!  Plan your Flights in Trips. Save and Share your Plane timings Information via Email, Text Message, Facebook, Twitter and WhatsApp Be able to adjust your plans on time. Traveling has never been so easy and comfortable as it becomes with Live Flight Status Tracker and Airplane Radar you can easily visit global cities such as New York, Tokyo, Washington, D.C, Los Angeles, San Francisco or London.
Uncover the mysteries of live air traffic in one beautiful and easy to use app Live Flight Status Tracker and Airplane Radar & Plane Finder can tell you exactly which plane it is. Detailed Status update and see the actual Plane paths Keeps you informed of changes and delays. Flight status Tracker provides live status updates 24/7 across the world. Easy to search for individual status and history track it by number or by route, Bar Code Scanner and by Country tracking. Detailed Departure and Arrival information by using the best app Live Flight Status Tracker and Airplane Radar We continuously work hard to maintain and keep the app running smoothly at its top performance for you! . We are passionate about providing innovative flight status and tracking apps giving you the information you need to make your travel smoother. ALERTS BY PUSH/FCM Firebase NOTIFICATION FOR: Scheduled & Actual Departure or Arrival Time Changes Gate and Terminal Changes, Flight Status Changes, You can Also Schedule Departure/Arrival Reminders by using this useful app Live Flight Status Tracker and view your Airplane by Radar. You can see Map of all Flights to and From an Airport. If you want to pick up relatives and family, switch to 'Arrivals' mode to check actual arrival time and terminal.
Track your flights with Plane Tracker app to save time and make your traveling stress-free. Access everything you need to know about your Plane, the airport, departure, arrivals, my-flights schedules and airlines in one easy-to-use app. You can easily track your flights by country tracking and save them in archive or favorite them to track flights any time you want. Where available, you can view arrival and departure boards, airport delay information. UPGRADE TO PRO VERSION: Unlimited flight search, status and tracking updates & No advertising banners at all.
Top Key Features of Live Flight Status Tracker and Air Plane Radar are :-
The Flight Status Tracker : Track Plane all over the World
Flight Schedules : Plots the where the actual Plane track and updates you with latest arrival time
My Flights : Near me, Track by simply scanning the Barcode & Search Planes
By Country :  Track any Plane Worldwide & Flight Board of all Departures/Arrivals per Airport.
Altitude Meter : Check altitude wherever you are in the Plane!
Archive : All Flights you track are save in archive folder
Famous Airports : This is a list of All International Airports by country & Cites.
Air Distance : Measure any distance on the map BTW two points.
